 id="fun-info0"><div class="info-box"><div id="fun-info2"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhQABAAIAAAMXFxQAAACH5BAAAAAAALAAAAABAAEAAAAJFhI+py+0Po5y02ouz3rz7D4biSJbmiabqyrbuC8fyTNf2jef6zvf+DwwKh8Si8YhMKpfMpvMJjUqn1Kr1is1qt9yuF1AAADs=" lazyload="images/fun-icon.svg" style="width: 100%; height: auto;" width="0" height="0"></div><div id="fun-info3">When you enjoy what you do, work becomes play</div><div class="more-info-text">Never get bored with the brand new way to design websites. Triangle features a lightning-fast development environment furnished with smooth animations and simple menus, making for an enjoyable way to make your clients happy.</div><a href="#"><div class="get-started-btn">Get Started</div></a></div></div></div><div id="customizable-info"><div id="customizable-info0"><div class="info-box"><div id="customizable-info2"><img src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhQABAAIAAAMXFxQAAACH5BAAAAAAALAAAAABAAEAAAAJFhI+py+0Po5y02ouz3rz7D4biSJbmiabqyrbuC8fyTNf2jef6zvf+DwwKh8Si8YhMKpfMpvMJjUqn1Kr1is1qt9yuF1AAADs=" lazyload="images/customizable-icon.svg" style="width: 100%; height: auto;" width="0" height="0"></div><div id="customizable-info3">Finally get full control over your website designs</div><div class="more-info-text">Triangle allows you to express your creativity in every way possible. Use Triangle's quick and versatile interface to move your ideas to the screen, or write your own CSS if that suits your style.</div><a href="#"><div class="get-started-btn">Get Started</div></a></div></div></div><div id="i38"><div id="i39">info@trianglecms.com </div><div id="i40">1-(909)-248-4024</div></div><div id="i41"><div id="i42"><div id="i43">TRIANGLECMS.COM Â© 2017 </div><div id="i44">INFO@TRIANGLECMS.COM</div><div id="i45"><span style="text-align: center;">1-(909)-248-4024</span></div></div></div></div><script type="text/javascript">document.body.onload = deferFonts;setTimeout(deferFonts, 2000);function deferFonts() { var defer = document.querySelectorAll("[defer]"); for (var i = 0; i < defer.length; i++) { defer[i].setAttribute("href", defer[i].getAttribute("defer")); }}</script><script type="text/javascript">document.addEventListener("scroll", lazyload);function lazyload() { var images = document.querySelectorAll('img[lazyload]'); var screenHeight = window.innerHeight; for (var i = 0; i < images.length; i++) { if (images[i].getBoundingClientRect().top < screenHeight + 300) { images[i].src = images[i].getAttribute("lazyload"); images[i].removeAttribute("lazyload"); } }}lazyload();</script><script type="text/javascript">var fastIcon = document.getElementById("fast-icon");fastIcon.addEventListener("click", function(){toggleInfo("fast")});fastIcon.addEventListener("mouseover", function(){animate("fast-icon", "shadowIn")});fastIcon.addEventListener("mouseout", function(){animate("fast-icon", "shadowOut")});var funIcon = document.getElementById("fun-icon");funIcon.addEventListener("click", function(){toggleInfo("fun")});funIcon.addEventListener("mouseover", function(){animate("fun-icon", "shadowIn")});funIcon.addEventListener("mouseout", function(){animate("fun-icon", "shadowOut")});var customIcon = document.getElementById("customizable-icon");customIcon.addEventListener("click", function(){toggleInfo("customizable")});customIcon.addEventListener("mouseover", function(){animate("customizable-icon", "shadowIn")});customIcon.addEventListener("mouseout", function(){animate("customizable-icon", "shadowOut")});var infoBoxes = ["fast", "fun", "customizable"];for (i = 0; i < infoBoxes.length; i++) { document.getElementById(infoBoxes[i] + "-info").addEventListener("click", function(){this.style.display = "none";});}function toggleInfo(name) { for (i = 0; i < infoBoxes.length; i++) document.getElementById(infoBoxes[i] + "-info").style.display = "none"; document.getElementById(name + "-info").style.display = "table"; document.getElementById(name + "-info").style.position= "fixed"; document.getElementById(name + "-info").style.zIndex = "2";}function animate(elem, animClass) { document.getElementById(elem).className = animClass;}</script></body></html>